  "text": "Following colony formation, MSCs were trypsinized, counted, seeded at density of 5000 cells cm 2 in 500 cm 2 triple flasks (Thermo Fisher Scientific), supplemented with hgDMEM, 10% v/v FBS, 100 U/ml penicillin, 100 μg/ml streptomycin, 2.5 μg/ml amphotericin B, and 5 ng/ml human fibroblastic growth factor-2 (FGF-2; Prospec-Tany TechnoGene Ltd., Israel) and expanded to passage 2 at 5% pO2. Tripotentiality was confirmed prior to use as previously described [CITATION_1] . ",
